{"tid":2496891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"文件揭港交所密集接觸華府六日","createTime":"2021-04-20T06:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T06:46:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82cda803841b078c2a6072b963451276af5c2737","tid":2496891,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:36:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/W5YVCY3PSZFA3CVBQ2W3ENOIIM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FW5YVCY3PSZFA3CVBQ2W3ENOIIM%2F&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuCNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=65a75f04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FW5YVCY3PSZFA3CVBQ2W3ENOIIM%2F&h=11268163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/W5YVCY3PSZFA3CVBQ2W3ENOIIM/</a><br />\n<br />\n文件揭港交所密集接觸華府六日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Rp8NcbpRYUluP4yAv-QeQWjy-TM=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XVEUM74H2FDM3CP55SJH6MEAOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRp8NcbpRYUluP4yAv-QeQWjy-TM%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXVEUM74H2FDM3CP55SJH6MEAOA.jpg&h=2baacde5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港交所代表曾多番電郵美國眾院議長佩洛西（左圖）及參院領袖麥康奈爾（右圖），最終跟前者會面。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特區政府在美國經說客安排「政治活動」，參與機構除了貿易發展局，香港交易所亦有牽涉其中。根據美國司法部資料庫，其中一份文件披露港交所透過同時受聘於伊拉克政府的Holly Strategies Incorporated為說客代表，前年9月25日至10月2日間一連六個工作天跟華府多個組織、部門及政治人物密集式接觸。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：聘美說客反《人權民主法》 港府白耗8,400萬<br />\n<br />\n文件顯示，接觸包括一次電郵眾議院軍事委員會、。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報稱商收購倫交所事宜<br />\n<br />\n最矚目的會面，對方為美國總統行政辦公室，接洽人員為時任總統特朗普的特別助理Tim Pataki。上月被港府批評意識形態和政治存在偏見的美國傳統基金會（Heritage Foundation），亦有跟港交所會面。至於接觸原因，文件「申報」涉及港交所收購倫敦證券交易所事宜；翻查資料，當時美國參眾兩院的外交委員會剛分別通過各自版本的《香港人權與民主法案》，盛傳兩院將快速表決法案。<br />\n<br />\n港交所接受本報查詢時稱。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a1d83a95275b77c2bb8413bf502b56a5a3a04603","tid":2496891,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:44:19.000Z","msg":"XGZF原來係美奸"},{"pid":"6354de0d61e5763b4345be1916031ff2f6d698d0","tid":2496891,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:46:28.000Z","msg":"李小加勾結外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}